{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/object-oriented-programming/reset-an-inherited-constructor-property","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"object-oriented-programming","demoType":null,"title":"Resetuj nasleđeno svojstvo konstruktora","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Kada objekat nasledi <code>prototype</code> od drugog objekta, on takođe nasleđuje svojstvo <code>constructor</code> njegovog nadtipa.</p>\n<p>Evo primera:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">function Bird() { }\nBird.prototype = Object.create(Animal.prototype);\nlet duck = new Bird();\nduck.constructor\n</code></pre>\n<p>Međutim, <code>duck</code> i sve instance objekta <code>Bird</code> treba da pokazuju da su kreirane pomoću konstruktora <code>Bird</code>, a ne <code>Animal</code>. To možeš postići tako što ćeš ručno postaviti svojstvo <code>constructor</code> objekta <code>Bird</code> na sam konstruktor <code>Bird</code>:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"language-js\">Bird.prototype.constructor = Bird;\nduck.constructor\n</code></pre>\n</section>","id":"587d7db1367417b2b2512b86","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"<section id=\"instructions\">\n<p>Izmeni kod tako da <code>duck.constructor</code> i <code>beagle.constructor</code> vraćaju svoje odgovarajuće konstruktore.</p>\n</section>","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":301324,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/object-oriented-programming/reset-an-inherited-constructor-property"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function Animal() { }\nfunction Bird() { }\nfunction Dog() { }\n\nBird.prototype = Object.create(Animal.prototype);\nDog.prototype = Object.create(Animal.prototype);\n\n// Only change code below this line\n\n\n\nlet duck = new Bird();\nlet beagle = new Dog();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>Bird.prototype</code> treba da bude instanca objekta <code>Animal</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(Animal.prototype.isPrototypeOf(Bird.prototype));"},{"text":"<p><code>duck.constructor</code> treba da vrati <code>Bird</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(duck.constructor === Bird);"},{"text":"<p><code>Dog.prototype</code> treba da bude instanca objekta <code>Animal</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(Animal.prototype.isPrototypeOf(Dog.prototype));"},{"text":"<p><code>beagle.constructor</code> inapaswa kurudisha <code>Dog</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(beagle.constructor === Dog);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/#object-oriented-programming","dashedName":"reset-an-inherited-constructor-property","certification":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"object-oriented-programming","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/object-oriented-programming/add-methods-after-inheritance","prevChallengePath":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/object-oriented-programming/set-the-childs-prototype-to-an-instance-of-the-parent","id":"587d7db1367417b2b2512b86","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"const funModule = (function () {\n  return {\n    isCuteMixin: obj => {\n      obj.isCute = () => true;\n    },\n    singMixin: obj => {\n      obj.sing = () => console.log(\"Singing to an awesome tune\");\n    }\n  };\n})();","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/javascript-algorithms-and-data-structures/object-oriented-programming/reset-an-inherited-constructor-property"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}